{"tid":328451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一首心攰時可以聽嘅歌","createTime":"2017-07-19T14:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T23:43:29.000Z","uid":83560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04e922f7a2841eb0c4232c2dc51f56f7052c1ed3","tid":328451,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:50:00.000Z","msg":"心好攰好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都做唔好<br />\n<br />\n我的天 你可不可以暫時讓我睡<br />\n忘掉愛 尚有多少工作失眠亦有罪<br />\n但如果 但如果怨下去 或者<br />\n傻得我 通宵找誰接下去"},{"pid":"af86c2d39c3c891c103c3aee43187a2ad6d5cc10","tid":328451,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"5d693231e7e249d5ae727c8fe169a98d59d0ac47","tid":328451,"uid":49250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"也可以"},{"pid":"3970d75a38e8d093d86dc1e4f3f6db46e12d8b46","tid":328451,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>也可以</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c804bf34f6d5b2e4692c8ac10e9c639e26e5f2","tid":328451,"uid":27741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N-MgRkSh5Xk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN-MgRkSh5Xk&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b39433e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N-MgRkSh5Xk</a><br />\nAstronaut- Simple Plan<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Can anybody hear me<br />\nOr am I talking to myself<br />\nMy mind is running empty<br />\nIn the search for someone else<br />\nWho doesn't look right through me<br />\nIt's all just static in my head<br />\nCan anybody tell me why<br />\nI'm lonely like a satellite?<br />\n'Cause tonight I'm feeling like an astronaut<br />\nSending SOS from this tiny box<br />\nAnd I lost all signal when I lifted off<br />\nNow I'm stuck out here and the world forgot<br />\nCan I please come down, come down<br />\n'Cause I'm tired of drifting round and round<br />\nCan I please come down?<br />\nI'm deafened by the silence<br />\nIs it something that I've done<br />\nI know that there are millions<br />\nI can't be the only one who's so disconnected<br />\nIt's so different in my head<br />\nCan anybody tell me why<br />\nI'm lonely like a astronaut?</span>"},{"pid":"65e23bf220803065d996a505cbdf670e71498f48","tid":328451,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"人生海海"},{"pid":"dbf5a0baa1ebe68c481724a66d6a361350a2323d","tid":328451,"uid":27741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"咩事唔開心啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sad完就振作啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NG2zyeVRcbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNG2zyeVRcbs&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5429ae9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NG2zyeVRcbs</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\nHope this words are enough <br />\nFor you to be strong, my friend<br />\nDon't ever run away<br />\nFor every fear you face<br />\nYou will survive and be much more than you were<br />\nSometimes you fall before you rise<br />\nSometimes you lose it all to find<br />\nThe world's gonna try and knock you out<br />\nJust pick yourself up when you go down<br />\nYou've gotta keep fighting<br />\nAnd get back up again</span>"},{"pid":"27bf91e79f5f555a3ebc67720bfb57e19180e041","tid":328451,"uid":27741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩事唔開心啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sad完就振作啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"h