:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:10:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1AYeFtOv_cw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1AYeFtOv_cw&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6707f627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1AYeFtOv_cw</a>"},{"pid":"3e3c5c0a90c594d2f96405166910e45fed631ac4","tid":328451,"uid":31368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-b4ndR0SW6Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-b4ndR0SW6Y&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=91db395b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-b4ndR0SW6Y</a>望著海一片滿懷倦　無淚也無言<br />\n望著天一片　只感到情懷亂<br />\n我的心又似小木船　遠景不見　但仍向著前<br />\n<br />\n誰在命裡主宰我　每天掙扎　人海裡面<br />\n心中感嘆　似水流年　不可以留住昨天<br />\n<br />\n留下只有思念　一串串永遠纏<br />\n浩瀚煙波裡我懷念　懷念往年<br />\n外貌早改變　處境都變　情懷未變"},{"pid":"e2d71a4139f7081dec63612b812e684cb39a3812","tid":328451,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:24:44.000Z","msg":"發覺這世界永遠太少空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a8113abca5a9e62812eb613a0c688a96a66281","tid":328451,"uid":77731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:26:22.000Z","msg":"Liability - Lorde<br />\n<br />\nThey say, &quot;You're a little much for me<br />\nYou're a liability<br />\nYou're a little much for me&quot;<br />\nSo they pull back, make other plans<br />\nI understand, I'm a liability<br />\nGet you wild, make you leave<br />\nI'm a little much for everyone."},{"pid":"37b0d947d023f107089b0df92a0255fbe64d7a4a","tid":328451,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:43:29.000Z","msg":"一想起 再累也是要做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}